cu.explanation_en: Setting the NG AMF IP address to an invalid format like '999.999.999.999' will cause network interface configuration errors.

du.explanation_en: Setting absoluteFrequencySSB to a negative value like -1 will cause frequency configuration errors.
du.explanation_zh: 將 absoluteFrequencySSB 設定為負值如 -1 會導致頻率配置錯誤。
